---
const imgLogo = "/assets/figma/LogoBuilt.svg"
---
<section class="flex w-full justify-center flex-col items-center gap-4 lg:gap-6 px-6 py-8">

  <div class="flex items-center gap-2 lg:gap-4 border-2 border-black px-3.5 py-1.5 rounded-full">
    <div class="border-2 h-4 w-4 rounded-full border-black bg-red-500"></div>
    <span class="text-xs lg:text-base font-bold">GDG Sucre presenta</span>
  </div>

  <img alt="" class="w-full lg:max-w-4xl lg:my-8" src={imgLogo} />

  <div class="flex items-center gap-2 lg:gap-4 border-2 border-black px-6 py-2.5 rounded-full">
    <span class="text-xl lg:text-2xl font-bold">Sucre 2026</span>
  </div>

  <p class="text-base lg:text-xl">Dos días para aprender, construir y conectar con la comunidad que está armando el futuro con IA en Bolivia.</p>


  <div class="flex flex-col gap-4 lg:gap-6 items-center w-full lg:max-w-md">
      <a href="#registro" class="bg-[#1e1e1e] border-2 border-[#1e1e1e] px-6 py-5 rounded-full text-white w-full hover:bg-[#333] transition-colors text-center text-base lg:text-2xl font-bold">
        Quiero mi lugar →
      </a>
      <a href="#agenda" class="bg-white border-2 border-[#1e1e1e] px-6 py-5 rounded-full text-[#1e1e1e] w-full hover:bg-[#f0f0f0] transition-colors text-center text-base lg:text-2xl font-bold">
        Ver convocatoria →
      </a>
  </div>


</section>